Name: absl_algorithm_container
Description: Abseil algorithm_container library
URL: https://abseil.io/
Version: 20250512
Requires: absl_algorithm = 20250512, absl_config = 20250512, absl_core_headers = 20250512, absl_meta = 20250512, absl_nullability = 20250512
